<p><strong>1. What is Dreamschool?</strong><br>
Dreamschool is a network of quality, affordable in-home child care programs. We provide qualified child care providers with the support and tools they need to successfully start and run their own child care centres. At the same time, we connect parents with high-quality, affordable, reliable and convenient child care close to home.</p>

<p><strong>2. What is the Dreamschool model?</strong><br>
Dreamschool is designed with a child’s well-being in mind. We used the latest evidence in early childhood education and care and worked with experts in the field to design the Dreamschool model. To learn more, check out our <%=link_to 'About Us', about_path, class: 'faq_about_text'%> page. </p>

<p><strong>3. How can I sign up my child for Dreamschool?</strong><br> 
