<p><strong>5. Can the ratings of the provider be revealed before the visit?</strong><br>Unfortunately, the ratings cannot be provided until a visit to the provider occurs.</p>

<p><strong>6. How do you select your child care providers? What is the process?</strong><br>Your child’s well-being and safety is our #1 priority. This is why we have a thorough recruitment and vetting process to ensure that we answer all of your burning questions about your child’s day care provider.  Our process includes: </p>
<ul>
  <li>Police check </li>
  <li>First aid certification</li> 
  <li>Reference checks</li>  
  <li>Verification of educational and/or work experience</li> 
  <li>1:1 interview </li>
</ul>

<p>We also provide our care providers with training and 1:1 coaching support to set-up and maintain their daycare centre.</p> 
<p>Before your child is placed in a care provider’s home, we will share all the details and answer any questions you have.</p>
